	(text "COIL REQUIREMENTS (J5) - validated envelope, swept in calcs.py at 11000uF / 55V:\n  L >= 1 uH  AND  R_total >= 90 mOhm\n  (R_total = coil DC resistance + leads/lugs; keep leads short)\n  Validated default: 30T demo coil, 12.406 uH, 110 mOhm total\n  Below envelope the pulse can exceed the 600A switch design point - DO NOT FIRE."
